Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.51,0:00:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的快遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你振作起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能一直消沉下去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭基他們好像正停留在霧之海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河道正好轉向那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續前進就會經過他們附近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許也能瞭解一些情況
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願皮尼歐沒幹蠢事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家都平安無事就行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是海賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全艦團發佈非常警戒警報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:00:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向皮尼歐傳令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還是我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾中校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是中校嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你很有精神 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了你的求救信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過畢竟身處這顆星球的另一面 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以由我動身前去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當時需要進行通信管制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能到我這邊來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 雷德少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即刻回歸庫蓋爾隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海賊…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大 不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好還是逃吧 皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說逃 往哪逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是有這大炮和破廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他們來一發作為見面禮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰角OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 這樣總該有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道像雷一樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢這麼對待我的寶物！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼…破廢鐵？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是雷德少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自即刻起回歸人類銀河同盟軍指揮之下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德！ 破廢鐵！
