Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你加入之後 Machine Caliber就有了兩台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 現在執行策劃已久的大規模啟蒙計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對象就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:21:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…！
